# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [0.0.1-alpha.1] - 2019-07-22
- Initial alpha release

## [0.0.1-alpha.2] - 2019-07-23
- Generate checkboxes via provided configuration
- Allow for multiple styles and sizes of checkboxes

## [0.0.1-alpha.3] - 2019-07-28
- Integrate custom loaders
- Input elements should be atomic
- Rename letter spacing classes
- Fix bug with link colors
- Remove symbols
- Remove unit blocks
- Remove duplicate z-index classes
- Remove unnecessary list classes
- Remove unnecessary flex classes
- Refactor form sass for smaller output
- Add box shadows
- Allow for custom sass files

## [0.0.1-alpha.4] - 2019-09-30
- Fix group button styling
- Fix checkbox positioning
- Add input box shadow option
- Add flex display class
- Add flex box alignment classes
- Fix circle button sizing
- Ensure typography util classes are applied

## [0.0.1-beta.1] - 2019-10-07
- Add wysiwyg styles
- Add color hover states
- Add truncate class
- Add line-wide class (for wide line heights)
- Add flex box classes for different screen sizes
- Add flex box classes for handling text wrapping
- Add circle radius class
- Add background color focus states
- Optimize build size

## [0.0.1-beta.2] - 2019-10-10
- Update wysiwyg styles
- Images within radius circle class should be display block
- Fix syntax errors with ::before and ::after
